com.github.dandelion.core.asset

Class Asset

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.dandelion.core.asset.Asset
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Asset
extends Object
implements Serializable

    Representation of an asset.

    Contrary to a AssetStorageUnit, an Asset contains more fields because it has been resolved by the AssetMapper.

    Since:
    0.0.1
    Author:
    Romain Lespinasse, Thibault Duchateau
